commit.title: [ssr] Clean-ups in extended intro patterns
commit.message:
[ssr] Clean-ups in extended intro patterns

We avoid hi-jacking the IPatId type to represent block introductions.
Instead, we define a dedicated type used in IPatDispatch and IPatCase.

We also add some comments and make some names more explicit.
